lead_paragraph: Terron Ward ran for two touchdowns, possibly clinching his roster spot, and the Atlanta Falcons beat the Jacksonville Jaguars 17-15 on Thursday night in each team's final preseason game.

headline.print_headline: Terron Ward Runs for 2 TDs as Falcons Edge Jaguars 17-15
